=== 男同性恋角色 ===
蝙蝠侠漫画里的[[男同性恋|男同性恋]]角色包括{{Link-en|哈珀·罗|Harper Row}}的弟弟库伦<ref>{{cite news |last=Rogers |first=Vaneta |url=https://www.newsarama.com/21895-who-was-the-masked-man-capullo-sketch-raises-questions-about-lark-what-s-wrong-with-batman-s-arm.html |title=Who Was That Masked Man? CAPULLO Sketch Raises Questions About LARK, What's Wrong with BATMAN's Arm? |work={{Link-en|Newsarama|Newsarama}} |date=2014-08-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190415030806/https://www.newsarama.com/21895-who-was-the-masked-man-capullo-sketch-raises-questions-about-lark-what-s-wrong-with-batman-s-arm.html |archivedate=2019-04-15 |accessdate=2021-02-05 }}</ref>和超级英雄[[午夜战士|午夜战士]]。午夜战士出现于由{{Link-en|狂野风暴|WildStorm}}所出版的漫画书，这是{{Link-en|虚构作品中的平行宇宙|Parallel universes in fiction|平行宇宙}}中一个类似蝙蝠侠的超级英雄；但自从[[DC漫画|DC漫画]]于2011年9月推出[[新52|新52]]重启后，午夜展示就成为主流[[DC宇宙|DC宇宙]]的一份子<ref>{{cite web |author1=Charles Pulliam-Moore |title=DC's Midnighter is more than just a gay Batman |url=https://splinternews.com/dcs-midnighter-is-more-than-just-a-gay-batman-1793848180 |publisher={{Link-en|尖锐新闻|Splinter News}} |accessdate=2021-02-05 |archive-date=2020-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022183214/https://splinternews.com/dcs-midnighter-is-more-than-just-a-gay-batman-1793848180 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。午夜战士经常出现在由[[迪克·格雷森|迪克·格雷森]]出演的作品中，例如《{{Link-en|格雷森 (漫画书)|Grayson (comic book)|格雷森}}》和《夜翼》<ref>{{cite web |author1=Rich Johnston |title=So How Close Are Grayson And Midnighter In DC Rebirth? |url=https://bleedingcool.com/comics/so-how-close-are-grayson-and-midnighter-in-dc-rebirth/ |publisher={{Link-en|Bleeding Cool|Bleeding Cool}} |accessdate=2021-02-05 |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125061919/https://bleedingcool.com/comics/so-how-close-are-grayson-and-midnighter-in-dc-rebirth/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

而在电视剧《[[哥谭镇_(电视剧)|哥谭镇]]》中，[[企鹅人|企鹅人]]（奥斯华·科伯特）被描述成了一个同性恋者或双性恋者，这和其他作品对这个角色的处理方式有着明显的不同<ref>{{cite web |title=Penguin's Surprising New Love Interest on Gotham Revealed |url=https://comicbook.com/dc/news/penguins-new-love-interest-on-gotham-revealed/ |publisher=ComicBook.com |accessdate=2021-02-05 |archive-date=2021-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209171439/https://comicbook.com/dc/news/penguins-new-love-interest-on-gotham-revealed/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

